#: ../../talk/appearance.rst:3
msgid "Appearance"
msgstr "Dealramh"

#: ../../talk/appearance.rst:6
msgid "Compact view of conversations list"
msgstr "Radharc dlúth ar liosta comhráite"

#: ../../talk/appearance.rst:8
msgid ""
"Compact view hides last message preview in the conversation list, providing "
"a more focused interface."
msgstr ""
"Cuireann an radharc dlúth réamhamharc ar an teachtaireacht dheireanach i "
"bhfolach sa liosta comhráite, rud a chuireann comhéadan níos dírithe ar "
"fáil."

#: ../../talk/appearance.rst:14
msgid "Chat messages"
msgstr "Teachtaireachtaí comhrá"

#: ../../talk/appearance.rst:16
msgid ""
"Chat appearance settings allow you to customize the look of your "
"conversation chats. You can choose between classic list or message bubbles, "
"with your own messages on the side."
msgstr ""
"Le socruithe cuma an chomhrá, is féidir leat cuma do chomhráite a "
"shaincheapadh. Is féidir leat rogha a dhéanamh idir liosta clasaiceach nó "
"boilgeoga teachtaireachtaí, le do theachtaireachtaí féin ar an taobh."

#: ../../talk/appearance.rst:19
msgid ""
"You can change both settings from the ``Talk settings`` dialog in the "
"``Appearance`` section."
msgstr ""
"Is féidir leat an dá shocrú a athrú ón dialóg ``Socruithe cainte`` sa rannán"
" ``Dealramh``."
